{"type": "article", "id": 27178, "title": "动物书签", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702150557MzVj5b2qpkhoR4IL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>一个制作精美的书签可以给阅读体验增加不少乐趣，Peleg Design 就推出了两款动物书签。它们的下半部分与普通的书签无异，上半部分则特意做成突起，这样一来河马和鳄鱼看上去就好像潜在水下只露出脑袋一样。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01BKJ11SY/\">链接</a>购买到这款可爱的书签。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150554OtyZpdGxMmAlI8u4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63522885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150554QBWe6zFysMlUmgv1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.63522885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150555j7vbA0LNF2s5aHdO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150556SuZYdW1UQgqjIbA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}